The '''graceful honeyeater''' ('''''Meliphaga gracilis''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Meliphagidae]]. It is found in the [[Aru Islands]], southern [[New Guinea]], and [[Cape York Peninsula]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]] and subtropical or tropical [[mangrove forest]].<ref name="iucn status 12 November 2021" />
